    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "<style>\n/* Game data dashboard only (Overview panel): Grafana dark theme primary.blue (palette.blueDarkMain) */\n.rdg.rdg-dark {\n  --rdg-header-background-color: #3d71d9 !important;\n  --rdg-header-draggable-background-color: #325cbd !important;\n}\n</style>\n\n<h3>Game schema (<code>game</code>)</h3>\n<p>Each panel below is <strong>one</strong> table: <code>SELECT * … ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 200</code> (cursor table orders by session/table name).</p>\n<p><strong>Wrong panel titles?</strong> Names must match exactly, e.g. <code>game.biobase_cs2_movement_sample</code> (not <code>movement_stats</code>), <code>game.biobase_cs2kz_sqlite_cursor</code> (note <strong><code>kz</code></strong>), <code>game.biobase_cs2kz_player</code> / <code>run</code> / <code>jumpstat</code> — not <code>kz_client</code>. Wrong names cause SQL errors (red warning). <strong>Delete this dashboard → restart Grafana</strong> so file provisioning recreates it (or pull latest and restart).</p>\n<p><strong>Sessions</strong> live in <strong><code>public.biobase_cs2_match_session</code></strong>, not <code>game</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Quick counts</strong> = row counts + <code>ops</code> log lines; use <strong>Ops ingest</strong> dashboard for raw <code>ops.*</code> data.</p>",
        "mode": "html"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "bb-postgres" },
      "description": "Row counts per `game` table plus raw `ops` log lines.",
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "id": 8,
      "options": { "cellHeight": "sm", "footer": { "countRows": false, "reducers": [] }, "showHeader": true },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "bb-postgres" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2_game_event)           AS game_event,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2_movement_sample)        AS movement_sample,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2_round_stats)            AS round_stats,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2kz_sqlite_cursor)       AS cs2kz_sqlite_cursor,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2kz_player)              AS cs2kz_player,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2kz_run)                 AS cs2kz_run,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM game.biobase_cs2kz_jumpstat)           AS cs2kz_jumpstat,\n       (SELECT count(*)::bigint FROM ops.biobase_cs2_log_line)               AS ops_log_lines",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Quick counts",
      "type": "table"
    },
